{
  "stem": "13258.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then she went to-- well, she was here in America, New York, and then she went to Korea and to  Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we never saw each other a lot since we grew up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we had-- we had a-- big family, especially when we were living in Beuthen where my mother's family was.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father's family got kind of spread out a little bit over the world, mainly due to the fact that the border was drawn and Kattowitz became Poland.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But my mother had her mother and numerous uncles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my great-grandfather was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we would have Friday evening Kiddush and dinner in my grandmother's house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My grandfather had passed away in 1923, when I was little-- my maternal grandfather.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then we would go to my great-grandfather's house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were children, grandchildren, and great-grandchildren.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The house was full, and there were some very strict rules.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You never sat down on the place at the table where great-grandfather was sitting.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was a place reserved for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But he loved us kids.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He would take us to his little office, because he had the business adjacent to his apartment, and call us in and open his desk drawer and take out some chocolates for us.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "From very little ones to bigger ones, everybody came in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And of course, he would not smoke on Shabbos, but he had always a supply of big, black cigars.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then the men would come in, and he would pass out cigars to the men, which you were not allowed to smoke on Shabbos, of course.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But they could take home with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a big family there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a big family.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
